data.title: Beer, Wine, and Spirits
data.meta_description: With classic American chophouses in mind, Wissota features Certified Angus Beef, an excellent variety of seafood, and creative sides.
data.text:
Dark Side

Jp's Casper White Stout Stout - White / Golden / 6.1 ABV / 9.0 IBU / Stevens Point, WI 16oz Draft 9

Brewer's Reserve Cherry Kringle Stout Stout - Imperial / Double / 10.8 ABV / Amherst, WI Since the kringle is the official pastry of wisconsin we thought it was only fitting that we combine it with another wisconsin staple: door county cherries. these particular cherries come to us from our friends at seaquist orchards and provide a delightful zing to each sip. Much like our wonderful state this beer is a truly unique treat! 10oz Draft 12

Mudpuppy Porter Porter - American / 5.6 ABV / 29.0 IBU / Amherst, WI A robust / yet surprisingly refreshing porter / mud puppy is a favorite of dark beer lovers. Characterized by a thick / rocky head and luscious chocolate-like nose / the malty profile is balanced by liberal hopping for its style. 16oz Draft 9

Good Dog Porter Porter - English / 4.7 ABV / Allouez, WI 16oz Draft 9

Perky Porterâ„¢ Porter - English / 7.0 ABV / 30.0 IBU / Green Bay, WI 16oz Draft 8

Premium Root Beer Root Beer / Stevens Point, WI 16oz Draft 6

Lighter Side

Summer Shandy Shandy / Radler / 4.2 ABV / 14.0 IBU / Chippewa Falls, WI 16oz Draft 8

3 Sheeps Pils Pilsner - German / 5.3 ABV / Sheboygan, WI 16oz Draft 8

Honey Blonde Ale Honey Beer / 4.5 ABV / 12.0 IBU / Amherst, WI Made using real wisconsin honey / our honey blonde is a traditional cream ale featuring a breezy floral bouquet / subtle sweetness / and crisp / clean finish. When you're feeling like something a bit more refreshing / this little number is sure to please. 16oz Draft 9

Sun Beam Wheat Beer - American Pale Wheat / 4.7 ABV / 12.0 IBU / Oshkosh, WI 16oz Draft 9

Honey Wheat Wheat Beer - American Pale Wheat / 4.7 ABV / 12.0 IBU / Appleton, WI 16oz Draft 9

Wheat Wave Wheat Beer - Other / 5.0 ABV / Milwaukee, WI 16oz Draft 8
